data.description: Welcome Home to this modern style townhome, featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and 1,320 Sqft of comfortable living space. The first floor boasts an open floorplan with the kitchen overlooking the living area. The kitchen offers granite countertops, a newer dishwasher and plenty of counter space. Adjacent to the living area, you'll find a charming patio overlooking a pond, perfect for fishing enthusiasts! This cozy outdoor space offers an ideal setting for grilling, allowing you to relish the tranquility of the great outdoors.Walk upstairs to your oversized owner's suite, where serenity and comfort await. You will also find a generous sized walk-in closet, a private owner's bathroom with a stand-in shower, linen closet and vanity, perfect for unwinding after a long day. The additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed, and has its own full bathroom. Upstairs in the hallway, you will conveniently discover the laundry space.   Further enhancing the appeal of this townhome is the one-car garage which offers the option to build storage racks or shelves. There are also 2 additional parking spots.    Lakeview Commons also offers wonderful amenities such as a pool, play park and 2 fully stocked ponds that you and your family will be sure to enjoy!   Located in the charming community of Goose Creek, South Carolina, this townhome offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Whether you're settling into your first home, a transitional space, or your forever home, you'll instantly feel a sense of belonging. With easy access to shopping, dining, and major highways, everything you need is just moments away. Schedule your showing today!
